1
00:00:55,000 --> 00:01:00,000
The Story of Minglan

2
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:02,833
Episode 34

3
00:01:03,280 --> 00:01:04,584
Have a drink!

4
00:01:04,584 --> 00:01:05,240
Drinkï¼

5
00:01:08,440 --> 00:01:09,400
Second Brother Bai,

6
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:11,040
you should just stay

7
00:01:11,040 --> 00:01:11,839
at our Yuzhou longer.

8
00:01:12,130 --> 00:01:13,400
That General Xie

9
00:01:13,401 --> 00:01:14,760
depends on you now,

10
00:01:14,760 --> 00:01:15,920
and he won't rush you back.

11
00:01:16,160 --> 00:01:16,840
That's true.

12
00:01:18,120 --> 00:01:19,610
Hang out with us more.

13
00:01:19,610 --> 00:01:21,170
What's so great about that army camp there?

14
00:01:22,020 --> 00:01:22,700
If it's up to me,

15
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:24,160
we'd have the militia to write a letter

16
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:25,800
and ask for you.

17
00:01:26,360 --> 00:01:26,920
Geng,

18
00:01:27,880 --> 00:01:28,760
you're drunk.

19
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:31,520
My father can't keep him.

20
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:36,240
If we had known how severe this riot was

21
00:01:36,280 --> 00:01:37,200
in the south,

22
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:38,640
we should've gone with them together

23
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:40,040
to knock the rebels,

24
00:01:40,280 --> 00:01:41,880
instead of staying here

25
00:01:42,440 --> 00:01:43,120
in this small, stifling Yuzhou!

26
00:01:43,330 --> 00:01:44,173
You saw that I set a merit

27
00:01:44,173 --> 00:01:44,960
and got a title promotion,

28
00:01:45,360 --> 00:01:46,360
so you're jealous.

29
00:01:47,520 --> 00:01:49,040
I'd love to have you come too actually,

30
00:01:49,240 --> 00:01:50,640
but your madam won't agree.

31
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:51,899
Lingnan is full of high hills

32
00:01:51,899 --> 00:01:52,520
dangerous waters,

33
00:01:52,800 --> 00:01:54,203
and lots of poison and malaria.

34
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:55,920
If your madam finds out,

35
00:01:56,160 --> 00:01:57,280
she'll eat me.

36
00:02:01,080 --> 00:02:02,080
You men

37
00:02:02,368 --> 00:02:03,160
have the grief

38
00:02:03,320 --> 00:02:05,160
of having tigresses at home.

39
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:06,120
Watching the house so tight,

40
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:07,080
so where do you even want to go?

41
00:02:07,640 --> 00:02:08,400
I think

42
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:09,880
my madam is the virtuous one.

43
00:02:10,160 --> 00:02:10,600
I'll come with you.

44
00:02:17,040 --> 00:02:18,000
Here, let me pour for you.

45
00:02:18,480 --> 00:02:20,040
Don't leave after we finish the meal.

46
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:21,360
I need to talk to you.

47
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:25,840
Here. Eat the food!

48
00:02:26,730 --> 00:02:28,400
Do you have news of Chang?

49
00:02:30,040 --> 00:02:31,200
If that were the case,

50
00:02:31,440 --> 00:02:32,920
why would I evade the others?

51
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:34,480
I would've drummed

52
00:02:34,571 --> 00:02:36,000
to celebrate already.

53
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:39,240
I asked my Canal Gang buddies

54
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:40,920
on my trip to the south too.

55
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:43,480
But there's no news still.

56
00:02:44,660 --> 00:02:46,600
Don't rush. The future has a long way to go.

57
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:47,876
After some time,

58
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:49,080
I'll find someone

59
00:02:49,080 --> 00:02:50,544
to look into the west side.

60
00:02:51,320 --> 00:02:52,200
Your Manniang

61
00:02:52,480 --> 00:02:54,024
is Chang's real mother after all.

62
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,840
She won't mistreat him.

63
00:02:59,480 --> 00:03:00,080
I hope so.

64
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:01,360
For now,

65
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:03,400
I have an important matter

66
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:04,560
to discuss with you.

67
00:03:04,910 --> 00:03:06,080
A few days ago,

68
00:03:06,379 --> 00:03:07,760
you got

69
00:03:07,920 --> 00:03:08,890
a promotion command.

70
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:10,520
For me,

71
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:12,840
I got a secret Imperial edict!

72
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:15,320
Secret Imperial edict?

73
00:03:16,896 --> 00:03:17,272
About what?

74
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:19,800
His Majesty first

75
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:20,988
praised us,

76
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:23,600
saying we are diligent and loyal,

77
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:26,720
Sage and merit-bound.

78
00:03:27,720 --> 00:03:28,880
Then he mentioned

79
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:29,451
how his health is just

80
00:03:29,451 --> 00:03:29,960
getting worse by the day,

81
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:31,999
and in the future when a new emperor ascends,

82
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:33,565
he wants us, father and son,

83
00:03:33,565 --> 00:03:34,720
both to assist with all our might,

84
00:03:35,160 --> 00:03:36,960
and we will have a great future ahead.

85
00:03:39,880 --> 00:03:41,520
So the Crown Prince has been selected?

86
00:03:44,920 --> 00:03:46,720
His Majesty is entrusting to cares everywhere

87
00:03:47,440 --> 00:03:49,200
to pave the way for the new emperor in the future.

88
00:03:50,320 --> 00:03:50,880
My father and I are of the bloodline

89
00:03:50,880 --> 00:03:52,080
of Emperor Taizong,

90
00:03:52,440 --> 00:03:53,440
so we have been a cold house for years.

91
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:55,360
Even if we have a friend like you with us,

92
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:57,000
we can only recommend you out

93
00:03:57,200 --> 00:03:59,280
so we don't court the suspicion of others.

94
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:02,040
Now he's sent us

95
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:03,273
this edict especially.

96
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:04,600
My father hasn't slept

97
00:04:04,776 --> 00:04:05,665
in many nights.

98
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:09,200
You are from the Dongjing precinct,

99
00:04:09,640 --> 00:04:10,720
so do you know anything?

100
00:04:12,440 --> 00:04:13,400
I think

101
00:04:13,731 --> 00:04:14,838
you needn't worry too much.

102
00:04:15,640 --> 00:04:16,825
Even if His Majesty is trying to

103
00:04:16,825 --> 00:04:17,880
restrain the Imperial clans,

104
00:04:18,880 --> 00:04:20,360
the first ones to clean up

105
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:22,440
are the few in Bianjing.

106
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:24,200
Those are the big trees

107
00:04:24,525 --> 00:04:26,423
who have the power to fight for the throne.

108
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:29,240
Yuzhou is no pivotal army command

109
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:31,266
nor some affluent area.

110
00:04:31,840 --> 00:04:33,320
Even if the intention were here,

111
00:04:33,520 --> 00:04:36,000
I'm afraid that the capital was not enough.

112
00:04:37,050 --> 00:04:38,760
That's what I said too.

113
00:04:39,080 --> 00:04:40,160
But for my father,

114
00:04:40,320 --> 00:04:41,526
you know how he is even if I don't say it.

115
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:42,811
I might not say these as a son.

116
00:04:43,320 --> 00:04:44,800
But he is too timid to go out

117
00:04:44,840 --> 00:04:45,920
if it's raining heavily outside.

118
00:04:46,160 --> 00:04:48,440
He's afraid the rain will crack his head.

119
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:51,400
Now a secret Imperial edict came,

120
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:54,840
and my father was

121
00:04:54,880 --> 00:04:56,000
truly not at ease.

122
00:05:00,440 --> 00:05:01,280
How about this?

123
00:05:02,280 --> 00:05:03,240
It's not too busy

124
00:05:03,280 --> 00:05:04,160
at Xie's command right now,

125
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:05,280
so I'll stay.

126
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:06,600
I'll be your father's little servant

127
00:05:06,720 --> 00:05:07,880
to guard

128
00:05:08,253 --> 00:05:09,341
and help him watch the house.

129
00:05:09,640 --> 00:05:10,400
How's that?

130
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:11,880
The hell with that!

131
00:05:11,891 --> 00:05:13,120
You're a newly

132
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:13,920
promoted officer

133
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:14,876
and you'll work as a servant?

134
00:05:15,400 --> 00:05:16,160
Although my father and I

135
00:05:16,280 --> 00:05:17,560
have a bit of hereditary nobility,

136
00:05:18,080 --> 00:05:20,480
we can't afford you.

137
00:05:24,640 --> 00:05:25,960
Then seal the house,

138
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:28,120
and hire a few extra guards to watch.

139
00:05:28,610 --> 00:05:30,200
Tell your father to sleep with ease.

140
00:05:30,280 --> 00:05:31,200
I've got everything.

141
00:05:31,960 --> 00:05:34,560
If the summons from the capital hasn't come,

142
00:05:35,160 --> 00:05:36,480
then nothing's the matter.

143
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:38,600
When the summons comes,

144
00:05:39,960 --> 00:05:41,080
we'll make our plans then.

145
00:05:43,130 --> 00:05:45,360
Where can I find some new guards

146
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:46,360
to watch this manor?

147
00:05:46,520 --> 00:05:47,680
If we don't know their background thoroughly,

148
00:05:47,880 --> 00:05:49,360
it's just planting trouble.

149
00:05:50,320 --> 00:05:51,360
I saw so many unfamiliar faces

150
00:05:51,369 --> 00:05:52,720
when I arrived earlier.

151
00:05:53,320 --> 00:05:54,160
I thought

152
00:05:54,160 --> 00:05:55,480
they were your servants.

153
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:57,400
They are not new?

154
00:06:01,280 --> 00:06:02,240
Come here!

155
00:06:02,880 --> 00:06:03,705
Brother Bai?

156
00:06:04,410 --> 00:06:05,680
Did you see a few new faces,

157
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:06,640
dressed as household servants

158
00:06:06,640 --> 00:06:07,480
about my height?

159
00:06:07,520 --> 00:06:08,640
I did see some new faces

160
00:06:08,640 --> 00:06:10,268
and they are from the pub, delivering food.

161
00:06:10,690 --> 00:06:11,850
They said they're leaving right away,

162
00:06:11,869 --> 00:06:12,970
so I didn't ask much.

163
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:14,520
Which direction did they go?

164
00:06:14,760 --> 00:06:15,640
To the east.

165
00:06:15,645 --> 00:06:16,594
The militia went with them right behind.

166
00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:19,760
The militia said

167
00:06:19,760 --> 00:06:20,680
they're going to

168
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:21,840
check the farmstead.

169
00:06:22,050 --> 00:06:22,800
Crap.

170
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:24,800
What's wrong?

171
00:06:25,400 --> 00:06:26,640
Hurry and get the horses!

172
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:13,280
The most beautiful thing on earth

173
00:07:13,280 --> 00:07:14,760
isn't the high summit or the beautiful water.

174
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:17,360
It's these grain fields.

175
00:08:17,440 --> 00:08:18,240
With these,

176
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:20,840
Yuzhou will be secure.

177
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:16,560
Sir

178
00:09:16,726 --> 00:09:18,683
Zhonghuai, you're finally here!

179
00:09:19,400 --> 00:09:20,080
Watch out.

180
00:09:41,880 --> 00:09:42,640
Move!

181
00:10:47,760 --> 00:10:49,320
Speak! Who sent you?

182
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:51,880
Father. Father.

183
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:54,360
Father, are you alright?

184
00:10:55,056 --> 00:10:55,610
Hurry and get up.

185
00:10:57,160 --> 00:10:58,000
Zhonghuai, he's going to kill himself!

186
00:11:04,170 --> 00:11:05,000
Men!

187
00:11:05,640 --> 00:11:06,560
Take him to interrogate!

188
00:11:36,452 --> 00:11:37,252
Let's go.

189
00:12:00,760 --> 00:12:01,720
You won't talk,

190
00:12:02,680 --> 00:12:03,621
and you'll have to suffer

191
00:12:03,621 --> 00:12:05,040
some skin and flesh pain.

192
00:12:11,520 --> 00:12:13,360
I know you're all suicide fighters.

193
00:12:14,880 --> 00:12:16,160
Even if the knife is cutting into your neck,

194
00:12:16,207 --> 00:12:17,215
you won't blink.

195
00:12:18,280 --> 00:12:19,200
However,

196
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:22,080
what I want today isn't your life.

197
00:12:23,880 --> 00:12:24,960
It's your guts.

198
00:12:48,080 --> 00:12:49,000
You won't talk,

199
00:12:50,280 --> 00:12:51,840
and I'll use these tools

200
00:12:52,047 --> 00:12:53,680
and try each one on you.

201
00:12:56,120 --> 00:12:56,720
If you're not dead yet

202
00:12:56,760 --> 00:12:57,680
by then,

203
00:13:01,560 --> 00:13:03,120
I'll use this knife

204
00:13:04,400 --> 00:13:05,760
and cut off your flesh,

205
00:13:05,760 --> 00:13:07,400
one piece at a time.

206
00:13:15,680 --> 00:13:17,200
I've got life preserving ginseng soup too

207
00:13:17,885 --> 00:13:19,368
to keep you alive.

208
00:13:22,640 --> 00:13:23,960
A butcher lived across my home.

209
00:13:25,640 --> 00:13:27,840
Since I was little, I watched him butcher animals.

210
00:13:31,410 --> 00:13:33,463
Sometimes,

211
00:13:33,463 --> 00:13:35,800
in order to keep the meat fresh for one day,

212
00:13:37,920 --> 00:13:39,760
he'd keep the animal alive.

213
00:13:41,720 --> 00:13:43,520
These tricks, I know them all.

214
00:13:47,040 --> 00:13:48,120
If you don't believe me,

215
00:13:50,680 --> 00:13:51,760
you can try it.

216
00:13:57,040 --> 00:13:58,240
The meat on the chest is the thickest.

217
00:13:59,960 --> 00:14:01,760
Even when you cut it a hundred times

218
00:14:01,760 --> 00:14:03,840
you only get half a bowl of blood.

219
00:14:05,600 --> 00:14:07,200
So we'll start from here then.

220
00:14:14,080 --> 00:14:14,800
It's Prince Yan!

221
00:14:16,160 --> 00:14:16,960
It's

222
00:14:18,080 --> 00:14:20,000
it's His Highness Prince Yan!

223
00:14:20,720 --> 00:14:21,920
He sent us.

224
00:14:28,520 --> 00:14:29,705
You should've told me sooner

225
00:14:29,705 --> 00:14:31,600
so I wouldn't have to exhaust all this energy.

226
00:14:39,160 --> 00:14:40,080
Why?

227
00:14:42,840 --> 00:14:44,840
Prince Yan and I have no grudges

228
00:14:44,840 --> 00:14:46,480
so why does he want to kill me?

229
00:14:49,040 --> 00:14:50,840
We only just received the secret Imperial edict

230
00:14:51,520 --> 00:14:53,200
and he sends the assassins.

231
00:14:54,760 --> 00:14:56,680
I fear it's about installing the royal heir.

232
00:14:57,000 --> 00:14:57,672
How does installing the royal heir

233
00:14:57,672 --> 00:14:58,280
have anything to do with me?

234
00:15:02,160 --> 00:15:03,440
Even though I'm an Imperial clansman,

235
00:15:04,680 --> 00:15:05,840
I was not born into the high nobility

236
00:15:05,840 --> 00:15:07,160
and I have no vast connections.

237
00:15:07,400 --> 00:15:09,080
With what would I fight with Prince Yan

238
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:10,560
and why does he oppose me?

239
00:15:13,160 --> 00:15:13,600
I'm afraid

240
00:15:14,800 --> 00:15:16,120
it must be because

241
00:15:16,480 --> 00:15:16,881
Prince Yan thought,

242
00:15:16,881 --> 00:15:17,960
that Imperial edict to be on standby for assistance

243
00:15:18,800 --> 00:15:20,680
was actually a Crown Prince installation edict.

244
00:15:23,200 --> 00:15:24,680
Now the matter of naming the royal successor

245
00:15:24,680 --> 00:15:25,520
is causing huge chaos

246
00:15:25,520 --> 00:15:26,760
in Bianjing.

247
00:15:27,240 --> 00:15:29,680
Prince Yan already has his own army ready.

248
00:15:29,681 --> 00:15:30,600
Any slight movement,

249
00:15:30,880 --> 00:15:32,360
and he will think it's real.

250
00:15:40,200 --> 00:15:41,480
I seal my house and sit at home,

251
00:15:42,240 --> 00:15:43,680
but the calamity falls from sky.

252
00:15:46,080 --> 00:15:47,480
Maybe

253
00:15:48,500 --> 00:15:50,320
I should go hide in the farmstead

254
00:15:50,320 --> 00:15:51,360
outside the city for a few days.

255
00:15:51,880 --> 00:15:52,800
You can tell them I went to live

256
00:15:52,800 --> 00:15:54,640
in the Buddhist monastery outside the city.

257
00:15:55,600 --> 00:15:57,240
If more assassins come,

258
00:15:58,120 --> 00:15:59,560
we can at least have some countermeasure.

259
00:16:00,960 --> 00:16:01,520
Father.

260
00:16:03,800 --> 00:16:04,851
We are of the bloodline

261
00:16:04,851 --> 00:16:05,560
of the great ancestors,

262
00:16:05,600 --> 00:16:06,560
descendants of the Imperial family.

263
00:16:06,800 --> 00:16:07,960
To be this scared

264
00:16:09,120 --> 00:16:10,920
isn't this a joke to others?

265
00:16:11,160 --> 00:16:12,640
What do you people know?

266
00:16:15,920 --> 00:16:17,680
Preserving your life is what matters.

267
00:16:22,040 --> 00:16:23,000
Sir.

268
00:16:23,000 --> 00:16:25,080
Since Prince Yan is already thinking that it's real,

269
00:16:25,960 --> 00:16:27,640
he would rather

270
00:16:27,640 --> 00:16:28,960
kill mistakenly than to not kill.

271
00:16:30,090 --> 00:16:31,160
If he wants to kill you,

272
00:16:32,040 --> 00:16:33,240
you can't hide anywhere.

273
00:16:40,890 --> 00:16:41,760
I think

274
00:16:42,640 --> 00:16:43,920
we go the whole hog to

275
00:16:46,120 --> 00:16:47,160
go to Bianjing

276
00:16:47,960 --> 00:16:49,123
and see His Majesty.

277
00:16:49,123 --> 00:16:50,280
Tattle on him!

278
00:16:51,040 --> 00:16:51,800
Tattle?

279
00:16:53,000 --> 00:16:54,400
Since we can't protect ourselves,

280
00:16:54,960 --> 00:16:55,960
why not attack as our defense?

281
00:16:56,840 --> 00:16:58,600
Instead of sitting here waiting to be killed,

282
00:16:58,600 --> 00:17:00,080
it's better to take a risk to make a move.

283
00:17:01,240 --> 00:17:02,960
We go to Bianjing furtively

284
00:17:02,960 --> 00:17:03,760
and meet His Majesty.

285
00:17:04,000 --> 00:17:05,400
Make public

286
00:17:05,400 --> 00:17:06,520
the evil deeds of Prince Yan.

287
00:17:07,600 --> 00:17:09,600
Even if we can't report his mistakes,

288
00:17:09,920 --> 00:17:11,240
